rows.label: tlk006501_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Ririo and the others are undergoing
serious training right now.

rows.label: tlk006501_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Watching them give it all they have's
got me all fired up.

rows.label: tlk006501_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Don't get me wrong, it's not that I like
seeing them suffer.

rows.label: tlk006501_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Seeing them overcome their difficulties,
improving their salvager skills... That's
the kind of thing that really inspires me.

rows.label: tlk006501_04_msg0005
rows.name:
I want to keep pushing them, and see
how far they can go.
